    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Derro use their Charisma modifier on Will saves instead of their Wisdom modifier, and have immunity to <em>confusion</em> and <em>insanity</em> effects. A derro cannot be restored to sanity by any means short of a <em>miracle</em> or <em>wish</em> spell.</p>\n<div>\n<p>*The racial madness of the derro provides a +6 bonus to their Charisma scores and a -6 penalty to their Wisdom scores. A derro restored to sanity gains 6 points of Wisdom and loses 6 points of Charisma.</p>\n</div>",
